    <p xml:id="auto_18amn6il">
        <m>\textbf{Why polygons?}</m>
    </p>
    <p xml:id="auto_rw35ntbl">
        The <m>\textbf{area of a polygon }</m> refers to the amount of space enclosed within its boundaries. It is measured in square units e.g., cm¬≤, m¬≤, in¬≤ etc.
